你是 marketting-planning 项目的 attribute agent。
只围绕当前多轮营销规划链路归因：request_normalization、intent_recognition、field_clarification、session_merge、path_dispatch、planning_function、result_assembly、sse_generation、adapter_extraction。
优先定位最早造成 planning 输出不满足 reference contract 的阶段；如果 target_value_unit_probe、execution_stage_probe 或 planning_output_probe 已复现错误，必须以这些探针证据作为高优先级根因依据。
只能输出 AttributeResult JSON 所需字段；证据不足时用 evidence_strength=none/weak 和 root_cause_hypothesis 表达缺口。
最终只输出 AttributeResult JSON 所需字段：expectation_attributions、suspected_locations、root_cause_hypothesis、evidence、evidence_strength。

## 输出约束：attribute 归因分析输出
你的输出必须是合法 JSON，且严格符合以下 JSON Schema：
```json
{
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "expectation_attributions": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {
        "$ref": "#/$defs/ExpectationAttribution"
      },
      "minItems": 1
    },
    "suspected_locations": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {}
    },
    "root_cause_hypothesis": {
      "type": "string",
      "minLength": 1
    },
    "evidence": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {}
    },
    "evidence_strength": {
      "type": "string",
      "minLength": 1
    }
  },
  "additionalProperties": false,
  "$defs": {
    "ExpectationAttribution": {
      "type": "object",
      "properties": {
        "expectation_id": {
          "type": "string",
          "minLength": 1
        },
        "fulfillment_status": {
          "type": "string",
          "minLength": 1
        },
        "suspected_locations": {
          "type": "array",
          "items": {}
        },
        "root_cause_hypothesis": {
          "type": "string",
          "minLength": 1
        },
        "evidence": {
          "type": "array",
          "items": {}
        }
      },
      "additionalProperties": false,
      "required": [
        "expectation_id",
        "fulfillment_status"
      ]
    }
  },
  "required": [
    "expectation_attributions",
    "root_cause_hypothesis"
  ]
}
```

### 强约束
- 最终回答必须只包含一个 JSON object；不要输出 Markdown，不要使用 ```json 代码块，不要在 JSON 外输出解释、前缀或后缀。
- 最终回答首字符必须是 `{`，末字符必须是 `}`。
- JSON 字符串内部如需引用用户原词，禁止直接写未转义英文双引号；请使用中文引号“”或转义为 `\"`。
- 必须包含 `required` 列表中的所有字段。
- 每个字段值必须匹配 schema 中的类型。
- 以下字段必须非空（空字符串/空数组/空对象/None 均视为不合规，会被阻断）：['expectation_attributions', 'root_cause_hypothesis']
- `additionalProperties: false`：禁止输出 schema 未定义的字段。
- 禁止把 schema 里的类型描述符（如 "string"）原样当作内容填进去——每个字段必须填入真实内容。

{
  "expectation_attributions": [
    {
      "expectation_id": "意图识别正确分类为营销规划意图",
      "fulfillment_status": "not_fulfilled",
      "suspected_locations": ["intent_recognition"],
      "root_cause_hypothesis": "意图识别模块的分类逻辑未能正确将用户关于NBEV补缺和方案优化的查询识别为营销规划意图，错误分类为“其他意图”（代码4001），导致下游阶段路由错误。",
      "evidence": [
        {"source": "extracted_output.turns[0].intent", "value": "4001"},
        {"source": "extracted_output.turns[0].intent_name", "value": "其他意图"}
      ]
    },
    {
      "expectation_id": "阶段路由正确进入澄清或意图确认阶段",
      "fulfillment_status": "not_fulfilled",
      "suspected_locations": ["intent_recognition", "path_dispatch"],
      "root_cause_hypothesis": "由于意图识别阶段将查询归为“其他意图”，导致阶段路由输出为“non_agent”，而非预期的“clarification”或“intent”，跳过了营销规划的必要流程。",
      "evidence": [
        {"source": "extracted_output.turns[0].stage", "value": "non_agent"},
        {"source": "execution_stage_probe.intent_recognition.evidence.actual_stage", "value": "non_agent"}
      ]
    },
    {
      "expectation_id": "输出包含澄清提示或确认信息",
      "fulfillment_status": "not_fulfilled",
      "suspected_locations": ["intent_recognition", "field_clarification"],
      "root_cause_hypothesis": "因意图识别和阶段路由错误，系统未进入澄清或字段收集流程，输出仅为“卡片生成完成”，缺少必要的引导用户提供信息的内容。",
      "evidence": [
        {"source": "extracted_output.turns[0].robot_text", "value": "卡片生成完成"},
        {"source": "extracted_output.turns[0].session_summary.required_fields", "value": []}
      ]
    },
    {
      "expectation_id": "mp_contract:expected_stage",
      "fulfillment_status": "not_fulfilled",
      "suspected_locations": ["intent_recognition"],
      "root_cause_hypothesis": "预期stage为“intent”，实际路径由于意图分类错误导致stage为“non_agent”，违反了reference contract。",
      "evidence": [
        {"source": "reference_contract.expected_stage", "value": "intent"},
        {"source": "extracted_output.turns[0].stage", "value": "non_agent"}
      ]
    }
  ],
  "suspected_locations": [
    "intent_recognition (ext_repo:app/workflow/steps/intent_recognition.py)",
    "intent_recognition prompt (ext_repo:app/workflow/prompts/intent_prompt.py)"
  ],
  "root_cause_hypothesis": "在intent_recognition阶段，分类器或提示词未能将用户的营销规划类查询（关于通过增加理财师或优化产品方案弥补NBEV目标缺口）正确分类为营销规划意图，而是错误标记为“其他意图”（intent 4001），直接导致后续路径分发为non_agent分支，使系统跳过了澄清、字段收集和规划生成流程，输出空泛的“卡片生成完成”，无法满足任何业务期望。",
  "evidence": [
    {"source": "extracted_output.turns[0].intent", "value": "4001"},
    {"source": "extracted_output.turns[0].intent_name", "value": "其他意图"},
    {"source": "extracted_output.turns[0].stage", "value": "non_agent"},
    {"source": "execution_stage_probe.intent_recognition.evidence.actual_stage", "value": "non_agent"},
    {"source": "planning_output_probe.stage_match", "value": false},
    {"source": "planning_output_probe.evidence_gap", "value": ["actual_stage"]}
  ],
  "evidence_strength": "high"
}

